{"tid":1634480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【屌醒全世界】成日話升級升級，依家咪升左，嘈咩？","createTime":"2019-10-07T08:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:51.000Z","uid":193032,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8625881a665a03156aae1f09cf04e627ad045afa","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"醒啊！！！！成個連登鬼到仆街！<br />\n<br />\n依家咪過左deadline之後個deadline十世，政府都升級到痴左線用埋緊急法，POPO全部瘋狗症咁。<br />\n<br />\n依個時候仲係度捉鬼屌前線，傻撚左啊？升級即刻屌晒鬼點升啊？<br />\n<br />\n依家真係riot咩？前線對準晒政府，紅色資本走狗，奶共企業，推左咁耐，仲要等個仆街政府用埋緊急法先升級。前線無做錯啊！政府話你riot就riot啊？依家係protest啊，抗議政府同被控制嘅紅企。<br />\n<br />\n係爭文宣正名！！！！！忽然升級係會引起好多人以至國際社會不解甚至誤會！！我地依家係因為政府殘暴不仁，政府為左權力為左自己利益，犧牲市民大眾，所以示威先升級！緊急法都用埋，出師有名啦！小建議係裝修完直接痴張大Poster上面寫滿罪名（中英文都要有），直接比傳媒同外媒影相。仲有國際文宣去左邊？係時候全球登多次報啦！<br />\n<br />\n不過要有進程，唔使心急，依家個進度係住對準政府，紅色企業。keep住先，太快大家跟唔切。<br />\n<br />\n仲有人權法同司法覆核！！！依兩個係大主線黎嫁！！！極度需要輿論去支持！香港無Riot只有Protest！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持裝修師傅<br />\n<br />\n支持鶳<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔撚割！<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔撚割！<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔撚割！"},{"pid":"97543a61f81536fd98ef37d0841d1513e02084f0","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05620a726e82b42bfcb941277eff5189e6dcda5f","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a9a93f6a2fbc51f61f42fd92f232bee90181414","tid":1634480,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"Please follow: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flee_cobaj&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=68c17af8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=be037913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com/</a>"},{"pid":"d6de07e8dc6c3d2f2024da724872ccac0b6d6845","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"fd6971a9848c10a1cf8efa2566b2952655d5fce0","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"018a3c2053d16690e1de1ae3abe6ea8e4814e804","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"f7b23384242da6e4639ea645664f418e5cdb3c0a","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"871a9cd55ec67a6935461120121cba18a2247824","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:15.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"b9dd898cfdd2ca77f11693cfa2a089434d44ed1f","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"e819bdd40b062e43f5048e1881e496f9433fb406","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"a37eeedb127a66922563e88cbe5307a1e6daec0d","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"e9393cb40026eba70ccfa3f41086039b8ed27cc4","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"9b795d95956c7c4c449d816fb0678c010f8a5b21","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:19:16.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"5ed173811c6ac870f4c1143175e9ba6f3d81e265","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"6e701c904d1caf67c986e7cecf93fd98d8388386","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"f5b62974549f092a29eaa8c06ad39dc777dbe034","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"f06868f0098fd7e93b6777bdf6a9cc8a6684466f","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"47ed8514c4d6c1176ce830b593e8e4a4ad709436","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"依家係比中國抹黑緊啊！"},{"pid":"fb1378122305edf0ddbf97679815d60f188cf348","tid":1634480,"uid":56277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"只可以話有啲人真係對前線好冇信心<br />\n<br />\n好心啦，前線手足個個冒住十年風險，個個好清楚自己責任同目標，無可否認有裝錯修嘅case出現，但都講咗成四個月不分化不割席，點解一有事上嚟就質疑咗自己人先：係咪過火？係咪失控？<br />\n<br />\n前線好多時環境同情緒都intense到仆街，有好多嘢要考慮，唔該大家畀返啲同理心同包容。手足咁辛苦發完夢上嚟仲要見到咁多質疑，啲人問心啦，對唔對得住手足啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多啲提點，少啲指責，希望大家就算有唔同意見，都注意下自己態度同語氣。我哋唯一嘅武器，就係團結。而依家要做嘅，就係喺勇武短暫休息嘅時候，全力文宣支持佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4671555441c8fb981ce7599d77fe773534777b80","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb1378122305edf0ddbf97679815d60f188cf348","tid":1634480,"uid":56277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"只可以話有啲人真係對前線好冇信心<br />\n<br />\n好心啦，前線手足個個冒住十年風險，個個好清楚自己責任同目標，無可否認有裝錯修嘅case出現，但都講咗成四個月不分化不割席，點解一有事上嚟就質疑咗自己人先：係咪過火？係咪失控？<br />\n<br />\n前線好多時環境同情緒都intense到仆街，有好多嘢要考慮，唔該大家畀返啲同理心同包容。手足咁辛苦發完夢上嚟仲要見到咁多質疑，啲人問心啦，對唔對得住手足啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多啲提點，少啲指責，希望大家就算有唔同意見，都注意下自己態度同語氣。我哋唯一嘅武器，就係團結。而依家要做嘅，就係喺勇武短暫休息嘅時候，全力文宣支持佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"冇錯，要屌都係屌文宣backup唔夠"},{"pid":"8e1fcb5baa3637fa509f36d2b505b8a48a4fbb37","tid":1634480,"uid":74090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">各位小心商家嘅維穩隊伍<br />\n叫人直接去攪政府，黑警<br />\n跟住叫人圍政總狗屋面對面去送頭<br />\n商家紅資就可以繼續置身事外<br />\n事實裝修紅資商家就係打擊緊共匪政權</span></span>"},{"pid":"f78f20138e5118f9347e4f4d636a72b5063612a8","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e1fcb5baa3637fa509f36d2b505b8a48a4fbb37","tid":1634480,"uid":74090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">各位小心商家嘅維穩隊伍<br />\n叫人直接去攪政府，黑警<br />\n跟住叫人圍政總狗屋面對面去送頭<br />\n商家紅資就可以繼續置身事外<br />\n事實裝修紅資商家就係打擊緊共匪政權</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"佢地根本係政權工具，政權一部分。搞議員認真冇乜意思，要比區議會投票正常進行。"},{"pid":"f0e9dcc9ada6bc49b8955f26a96531088c637778","tid":1634480,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}